##LightBlog

simple Blog in Python language and Easy development Because it uses a bottle framework .


##Instilling lib

sudo apt-get install mysql-server mysql-client
sudo apt-get install python-mysqldb
apt-get install python-setuptools
sudo easy_install bottle
sudo easy_install postmarkup
sudo easy_install PyRSS2Gen
sudo apt-get install python-imaging

##Run blog

-Create new database. 
{example"
mysql -u root -p
create database test;
"}

-Edit the file config.
edit config.py {Write settings, contact databases & Email & Cookies} 

-Run script file "install.py" for insert tables in database"
run in terminal{
python install.py
}

-Run script file "update.py" for update tables in database
run in terminal{
python update.py
}

-Run script file "main.py" for test
run in terminal{
python main.py
}

++OR++

Read the different methods of operation in the link.

http://bottlepy.org/docs/dev/tutorial.html#deployment

##url blog

http://127.0.0.1:8080/blog/

##admin panel

http://127.0.0.1:8080/blog/admin

